Wed Apr 19 12:11:47 2000  Carlos O'Ryan  <coryan@uci.edu>

        * examples/Simulator/Event_Supplier/DOVE_Supplier.cpp:
        * examples/Simulator/Event_Supplier/DualEC_Sup.cpp:
